{"tid":840651,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"唔抵得波波身材太勁？　麥明詩：你去做縮胸手術啦！","createTime":"2018-09-29T03:26:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T12:36:46.000Z","uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"89ff1d5052208bdfa2738d0756f2031277e2417b","tid":840651,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:26:17.000Z","msg":"大台節目《#後生仔傾吓偈》經常都會講到一啲較私人嘅話題，不過一班後生仔通常都百無禁忌，照講可也！呢集就講到女仔戴bra嘅問題，麥明詩語出驚人，竟然叫上圍谷爆嘅學生KOL「波波」去做縮胸手術！係咪唔抵得人哋身材好過自己太多先？<br />\n<br />\n成班男人問，女仔喺屋企係咪會唔戴bra？成班女仔異口同聲一齊答：「梗係啦！」<br />\n<br />\n馮盈盈再補多句：「梗係啦！強調咗無限咁多次喇！」睇嚟佢好憎戴bra喎！麥明詩話同波波曾經詳談「縮胸手術」嘅事！仲話：「我覺得佢可以考慮！」"},{"pid":"df5865d885b00fad5cea0a913baadf40a4a1759e","tid":840651,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:30:50.000Z","msg":"升球大墊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b713e0a3a555358c9cdc11f18b17e8b54c41aa","tid":840651,"uid":9286,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:33:12.000Z","msg":"成個節目除咗波波大胸<br />\n其他女全部都平胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eace28000df0a4881d866ddada1cdc9b85a2424","tid":840651,"uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"48b713e0a3a555358c9cdc11f18b17e8b54c41aa","tid":840651,"uid":9286,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T03:33:12.000Z","msg":"成個節目除咗波波大胸<br />\n其他女全部都平胸<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:47:19.000Z","msg":"即係好似D中學雞大熱天時要著冷衫先埋到堆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a30207296c3814c91471674d93a1103a5be4f8ca","tid":840651,"uid":168366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:48:47.000Z","msg":"有咩咁語出驚人<br />\n搞笑當認真"},{"pid":"0c07136c02ddaa85f063cd30beca858a7516885d","tid":840651,"uid":16624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a30207296c3814c91471674d93a1103a5be4f8ca","tid":840651,"uid":